msgid "Doctrine: Offensive"
msgstr "Doctrina: Ofensiva"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/lose_panthers"
msgid "You were unable to keep at least one Panther tank operational!"
msgstr "¡Has sido incapaz de mantener ni un solo tanque Panther en activo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/mission_option_select1"
msgid "Select your Doctrine for the mission:"
msgstr "Seleccione su Estrategia para la misión:"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/name"
msgid "Operation Lüttich"
msgstr "Operación Lüttich"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/name_big"
msgid "Operation Lüttich"
msgstr "Operación Lüttich"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/01"
msgid ""
"Before us stands the town of Le-Mesnil-Tôve. We must seize its vital "
"crossroads if we want Operation Lüttich to succeed!"
msgstr ""
"Ante nosotros está la ciudad de Le-Mesnil-Tôve. ¡Debemos tomar sus "
"principales accesos si queremos que la Operación Lüttich sea un éxito!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/02"
msgid ""
"The town is only lightly defended. I place our Panzeraufklärer under your "
"command! When you have captured the crossroads, our Panzers will roll in."
msgstr ""
"La ciudad no tiene una gran defensa. ¡Pongo a nuestros Panzeraufklärer a tu "
"disposición! Cuando hayas controlado el acceso, nuestros Panzers entrarán."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/03"
msgid ""
"You should be able to make quick work of the Americans, but you don't have a "
"lot of manpower. Advance cautiously and don't take unnecessary risks."
msgstr ""
"Deberías poder acabar rápido con los americanos, pero no tienes demasiados "
"efectivos. Avanza con cautela y no corras riesgos innecesarios."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/04"
msgid "Ah, look what the Americans left us! What a beautiful half-track!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ah, mira lo que nos dejaron los estadounidenses! ¡Qué hermoso semioruga!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/05"
msgid ""
"Good work, Soldaten! I will now dispatch a garrison to hold Le-Mesnil-Tôve. "
"But as for you, unfortunately you will not have much time to rest. I will "
"need you for further tasking in a couple hours!"
msgstr ""
"¡Buen trabajo, Soldaten! Ahora enviaré una guarnición para defender Le-"
"Mesnil-Tôve. Pero en cuanto a usted, desafortunadamente no tendrá mucho "
"tiempo para descansar. ¡Los necesitaré para más tareas en un par de horas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/06"
msgid ""
"The Panzergrenadiere from Kampfgruppe Zander have met resistance on the "
"approaches to Chérencé le Roussel in the north. I need you to assist them."
msgstr ""
"Los Panzergrenadiere del Kampfgruppe Zander han encontrado resistencia en "
"los accesos a Chérencé le Roussel en el norte. Necesito que les ayudes."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/07"
msgid ""
"I place some of our armor under your command. Keep the enemy pinned at "
"maximum range, where you will be impervious to their 57mm AT guns. "
msgstr ""
"Pongo algunos de nuestros blindados a su disposición. Mantenga al enemigo "
"inmovilizado al máximo alcance, donde será vulnerable a sus cañones AT de 57 "
"mm. "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/08"
msgid ""
"Enemy counterattack from the direction of Chérencé le Roussel! Deal with "
"those Americans, Herr Leutnant!"
msgstr ""
"¡Contraataque enemigo desde Chérencé le Roussel! ¡Acabe con esos americanos, "
"Herr Leutnant!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/081"
msgid ""
"Well done Herr Leutnant. Despite the effort, we have not reached Chérencé le "
"Roussel; US defenses have not collapsed, and the constant counter attacks "
"are grinding our offensive momentum to a halt. "
msgstr ""
"Bien hecho Herr Leutnant. A pesar del esfuerzo, no hemos alcanzado Chérencé "
"le Roussel; las defensas estadounidenses no se han derrumbado, y los "
"constantes contraataques están paralizando nuestra ofensiva. "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/09"
msgid ""
"..... Attention! The Americans are threatening Le-Mesnil-Tôve from our rear! "
"We cannot afford to lose this position! I order you to turn around "
"immediately! Come back to the town and reinforce the garrison!"
msgstr ""
"..... ¡Atención! ¡Los americanos amenazan Le-Mesnil-Tôve desde nuestra "
"retaguardia! ¡No podemos permitirnos perder esta posición! ¡Les ordeno que "
"den la vuelta inmediatamente! ¡Vuelvan a la ciudad y refuercen la guarnición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/10"
msgid ""
"We have further bad news. The attack of our neighoring unit has failed and "
"the remnants have returned here after a fighting retreat."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos más malas noticias. El ataque de nuestra unidad vecina ha fracasado "
"y los aliados restantes han venido aquí tras una dolorosa retirada."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/11"
msgid ""
"The Panthers need resupply and repairs. Moreover, we cannot afford to lose "
"more of them. Take good care of them, and quickly. We need at least one of "
"them going by the time this is over."
msgstr ""
"Los Panthers necesitan reabastecimiento y reparaciones. Además, no podemos "
"permitirnos perder ni uno más. Trátelos bien, y rápido. Necesitamos al menos "
"uno de ellos en marcha para cuando esto termine."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/12"
msgid ""
"In any case, back to the elephant in the room - we are encircled! Your new "
"objective is to defend these crossroads and fend off any american attacks at "
"sunrise!"
msgstr ""
"En cualquier caso, volvamos al tema principal: ¡estamos rodeados! ¡Vuestro "
"nuevo objetivo es defender estos accesos y rechazar cualquier ataque "
"americano al amanecer!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/13"
msgid ""
"We have received our last reinforcements, Herr Leutnant. Some engineers and "
"air defence trucks to bolster your defences. I suppose some AAA is quite "
"welcome, we expect the Americans to attack us from the air tomorrow."
msgstr ""
"Hemos recibido los últimos refuerzos, Herr Leutnant. Ingenieros y camiones "
"con antiaéreos para reforzar nuestras defensas. Algo de AAA siempre es "
"bienvenido, pues esperamos que los americanos nos ataquen desde el aire "
"mañana."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/narrator/sniper"
msgid "Attention! Enemy sniper on top of that grain silo!"
msgstr "¡Atención! ¡Francotirador enemigo encima de ese silo de grano!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Excellent work! The Oberkommando will be delighted with your leadership. We "
"might win the battle for Normandy after all, after which we’ll probably go "
"back to the eastern front to beat the Soviets. Good job!"
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo! El Oberkommando estará encantado con su liderazgo. "
"Después de todo, puede que ganemos la batalla de Normandía, tras lo cual "
"probablemente volvamos al frente oriental para derrotar a los soviéticos. "
"¡Buen trabajo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"This is very unfortunate indeed. We should have been en route to Avranches "
"but we aren’t. How are you going to explain this to the Oberkommando? You "
"will have to regroup and try again, with a bit more vigor!"
msgstr ""
"Esto es muy desafortunado. Deberíamos estar de camino a Avranches, pero no "
"lo hemos conseguido. ¿Cómo vas a explicar esto al Oberkommando? Tendrás que "
"reagruparte e intentarlo de nuevo, ¡con un poco más de vigor!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/place"
msgid "116th Panzer Division"
msgstr "116ª División Panzer"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/skip"
msgid "Skip preparation phase"
msgstr "Saltar la fase de preparación"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/story"
msgid " August, 1944. After the American breakthrough at St. Lô, Avranches has now fallen into American hands. German high command orders a counterattack in the direction of Avranches, hoping to cut off the allied advance. This counterattack, known as Operation Lüttich, aims to cut into the allied flank around Mortain.\n\n You’re a Panzer commander from 116th Panzer Division, and your battalion is attached to Kampfgruppe Schake for this mission. You have orders to advance and take Le- Mesnil- Tôve. Take the village and secure the area. There is little or no information on enemy disposition, so it’s up to your tactical insight and improvisation skill to achieve your goals. Move out immediately, establish contact with the Panzergrenadiers, and wait for further instructions.\n\nGood luck!"
msgstr ""
"Agosto, 1944.\n"
"\n"
"Después del avance americano en St. Lô,\n"
"\n"
"Avranches ha caído en manos americanas. El alto\n"
"\n"
"mando alemán ordena un contraataque en dirección\n"
"\n"
"a Avranches, con la esperanza de frenar el avance aliado.\n"
"\n"
"Este contraataque, conocido como Operación Lüttich,\n"
"\n"
"tiene como objetivo detener el flanco aliado alrededor de Mortain.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Eres un comandante Panzer de la 116ª División Panzer,\n"
"\n"
"y tu batallón está adscrito al Kampfgruppe Schake\n"
"\n"
"para esta misión.\n"
"\n"
"Tienes órdenes de avanzar y tomar Le- Mesnil- Tôve.\n"
"\n"
"Tomen el pueblo y aseguren la zona.\n"
"\n"
"Hay poca o ninguna información sobre la disposición del enemigo,\n"
"\n"
"así que dependes de tu perspicacia táctica y tu capacidad de improvisación\n"
"\n"
"para lograr tus objetivos.\n"
"\n"
"Muévete inmediatamente, establece contacto con los\n"
"\n"
"Panzergrenadiers, y espera nuevas instrucciones.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"¡Buena suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/task1"
msgid "Capture the vital crossroads at Le-Mesnil-Tôve "
msgstr "Capturar las principales encrucijadas de Le-Mesnil-Tôve "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/task2"
msgid "Attack to the north to support Kampfgruppe Zander from 116.PZD"
msgstr ""
"Ataquen hacia el norte para apoyar a Kampfgruppe Zander de la 116.ª División "
"Panzer"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/task2_1"
msgid "Eliminate checkpoint to the northeast"
msgstr "Eliminar punto de control al noreste"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/task2_2"
msgid "Eliminate checkpoint to the northwest"
msgstr "Eliminar punto de control al noroeste"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/task3"
msgid "Return to the crossroad to rescue the garrison "
msgstr "Volver a la encrucijada para rescatar a la guarnición "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/task4"
msgid "Defend Le-Mesnil-Tôve at all costs. "
msgstr "Defiender Le-Mesnil-Tôve a toda costa. "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/task_panthers"
msgid "Keep at least one Panther operational"
msgstr "Mantener al menos un Panther operativo"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/timer"
msgid "Prepare to defend the crossroads!"
msgstr "¡Prepárense para defender la encrucijada!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_08_07_luttich/timer2"
msgid "Defend the town against the American assault!"
msgstr "¡Defiendan la ciudad del asalto americano!"
